&#127926;Sittin on the dock at Beech Bay... &#127926;
Watchin the sun fade away... &#127926;&#9728;&#65039;&#128526;&#127907;
Looking for your waterfront home on the Albemarle Sound w expansive views day & night? Check this one out! Two living areas, two kitchens, 4 bedrooms, 3 bathrooms and a flex room! Attached garage & carport, large laundry room, upper deck w views of the water, plus a spacious sunroom! You will love the convenient cargo elevator too!  Plus this home has solar panels.  Storage building w covered area is perfect for lawn equipment. Broker/owner. Septic permit for 4 bedrooms. Neighborhood offers a sandy beach area.
